'''Vector Day''' was an annual holiday. [[Mrp-Mrp Poo]] was known to throw parties for this occasion at the [[Boulderdash]] terrarium.<ref name="Monsters and Aliens">''[[Monsters and Aliens from George Lucas]]''</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
Vector Day was mentioned in [[Bob Carrau]]'s ''[[Monsters and Aliens from George Lucas]]'', a book published in [[1993]].<ref name="Monsters and Aliens" /> [[Lucasfilm]] employee [[Leland Chee]], who maintains the [[Holocron continuity database]], has indicated that information contained in the book is [[Canon|non-canonical]].<ref name="Chee">{{SWBoards|url=thread.jspa?threadID=152583&start=690#14724917|thread=Holocron continuity database questions|user=[[Leland Chee|Leland Y Chee]]|date=2006-05-03|time=5:45 PM|quote=And is information from Monsters and Aliens from George Lucas canon? Unless referred to by a source that is in-continuity, the information is non-continuity.}}</ref>

